That kid is becoming more and more outrageous.

115
00:07:41,417 --> 00:07:42,817
Yes.

116
00:07:45,100 --> 00:07:47,350
Siyue, help me persuade him.

117
00:07:47,350 --> 00:07:48,750
All right.

118
00:07:51,220 --> 00:07:53,250
Auntie,

119
00:07:53,250 --> 00:07:55,130
let me talk to Jiang Chen.

120
00:07:55,130 --> 00:07:57,110
Right. You guys should talk.

121
00:07:57,110 --> 00:07:58,970
Don't be so stubborn.

122
