133
00:09:53,250 --> 00:09:54,780
What are you talking about?

134
00:09:54,780 --> 00:09:57,430
You are so mature.

135
00:09:57,430 --> 00:10:01,240
No wonder you can persuade Jiang Chen's dad.

136
00:10:01,240 --> 00:10:03,350
How did you manage to do that?

137
00:10:05,690 --> 00:10:09,820
It's not really a huge thing.

138
00:10:09,820 --> 00:10:14,530
I told his dad that the reason why Jiang Chen wants to be a soldier

139
00:10:14,530 --> 00:10:17,800
is because he wants to be someone as excellent as his dad.

140
00:10:18,610 --> 00:10:20,890
Impressive.

141
00:10:20,890 --> 00:10:23,000
You really do know your way around words.

142
