And it's super cheap.

157
00:11:04,740 --> 00:11:06,740
AlL right. Great.

158
00:11:08,740 --> 00:11:10,540
Jiang Chen.

159
00:11:10,540 --> 00:11:13,790
Keke, we'll leave now.

160
00:11:15,050 --> 00:11:16,030
What are you doing here?

161
00:11:16,030 --> 00:11:18,213
Waiting for you.

162
00:11:18,213 --> 00:11:20,013
You are waiting for me?

163
00:11:20,820 --> 00:11:23,122
Why didn't you put on more clothes?

164
00:11:28,250 --> 00:11:29,490
Tie it around your waist.

165
00:11:29,490 --> 00:11:31,520
It's corny. I don't want that.

166
00:11:31,520 --> 00:11:33,030
I'm going to the art class later.

167
00:11:33,030 --> 00:11:34,261
Put it on.

168
00:11:34,261 --> 00:11:37,072
- What are you doing?
 - It's cold today.

169
00:11:40,980 --> 00:11:42,740
Sticking your finger in every pie.

170
