Hop on, I'll give you a ride.

171
00:11:48,900 --> 00:11:50,700
Come.

172
00:11:54,300 --> 00:11:55,900
Fine.

173
00:11:57,740 --> 00:12:01,910
It's not bad to have a free ride.

174
00:12:04,740 --> 00:12:06,440
Hold on tight.

175
00:12:12,150 --> 00:12:15,530
You must have figured out which school you are going to.

176
00:12:15,530 --> 00:12:16,980
Of course.

177
00:12:16,980 --> 00:12:19,340
It would be the Acting Department of the Film Academy.

178
00:12:19,340 --> 00:12:21,828
If I can't succeed this year, I'll get it next year.

179
00:12:21,828 --> 00:12:24,000
I'll keep trying until I get in.

180
00:12:24,000 --> 00:12:25,780
