196
00:13:16,920 --> 00:13:18,690
I'd love to.

197
00:13:18,690 --> 00:13:22,150
But Huaqing is not giving me that chance.

198
00:13:24,220 --> 00:13:27,680
I would be happy if I could go to the same city.

199
00:13:29,980 --> 00:13:32,690
You guys have a chance to go to a university in the same city.

200
00:13:32,690 --> 00:13:35,590
