214
00:14:29,100 --> 00:14:30,930
Who told you that?

215
00:14:30,930 --> 00:14:32,300
I didn't write that.

216
00:14:32,300 --> 00:14:34,310
Someone else wrote it for me.

217
00:14:34,310 --> 00:14:37,440
