225
00:15:07,450 --> 00:15:09,750
but this motorbike.

226
00:15:09,750 --> 00:15:12,490
That's a surprise.

227
00:15:17,110 --> 00:15:18,910
Take it.

228
00:15:26,300 --> 00:15:29,200
I'll keep it safe for you...

229
00:15:30,103 --> 00:15:32,203
and wait for you to come back.

230
00:15:34,780 --> 00:15:36,480
Another thing.

231
00:15:38,440 --> 00:15:42,250
Break a leg in the exam tomorrow.

232
00:15:42,250 --> 00:15:45,220
You will get into the university you desire.

233
00:15:46,340 --> 00:15:48,660
