234
00:16:19,291 --> 00:16:22,230
Playing with you is boring.

235
00:16:22,230 --> 00:16:23,780
I would like to play with you.

236
00:16:26,370 --> 00:16:27,420
Are you sure?

237
00:16:27,420 --> 00:16:29,120
I'm sure.

238
00:16:29,120 --> 00:16:31,193
I think she and I are at the same level.

239
00:16:31,193 --> 00:16:34,420
Don't take this the wrong way. I just want you to take a break.

240
00:16:34,420 --> 00:16:36,243
All right.

241
00:16:37,250 --> 00:16:41,060
Here. Show him what you are made of.

242
00:16:49,300 --> 00:16:52,740
Are you that lucky?

243
00:16:57,610 --> 00:16:59,790
This is a coincidence.

244
00:17:10,200 --> 00:17:12,260
That dude is seeking failure.

245
00:17:12,260 --> 00:17:15,900
He thought Little Monster was soft.

246
00:17:15,900 --> 00:17:19,090
Little did he know that he picked on a hardcore.

247
00:17:27,040 --> 00:17:28,400
I thought you were leaving tonight.

248
00:17:28,400 --> 00:17:30,190
You still have the time to play it out in pool?

249
00:17:30,190 --> 00:17:34,880
