250
00:17:34,880 --> 00:17:36,970
And I got beaten hard.

251
00:17:36,970 --> 00:17:40,670
Come here and have something. The food might get cold.

252
00:17:40,670 --> 00:17:42,980
- All right. I'll finish a round.
 - Coming!

253
00:17:43,700 --> 00:17:46,300
- Come on, Brother Song.
 - Coming.

254
00:17:48,800 --> 00:17:53,100
Little Monster, you are so good at pool.

255
00:17:54,180 --> 00:17:56,350
