256
00:18:00,070 --> 00:18:04,370
Um... Do contact me often.

257
00:18:04,370 --> 00:18:06,180
- Okay.
 - Sure.

258
00:18:09,370 --> 00:18:13,680
Better yet, tell me things about Keke.

259
00:18:14,900 --> 00:18:18,910
